title: 2012 O'Neill Psycho 3 Wetsuit
description: The Psycho 2 was known for warmth, flexibility and superior fit. It has evolved into the totally mental Psycho 3. We've upgraded to the exclusive TechnoButter Neoprene. We've combined TechnoButter with XDS-Air Firewall in the chest and back, and Double SuperSeam Weld to keep you warm and loose. The latest evolution from Area 52 continues to be an industry leader and will keep you performing at the top of your game.
